$Id: INSTALL 2809 2015-03-10 20:47:00Z Colin $

---
Intro

1-.  RPM and yum based install is now available.

yum setup:

# rpm -i http://unixservice.com/rpm/i386/unxsyum-1.0-1.i386.rpm

# rpm -i unxsyum-1.0-1.i386.rpm
# yum search unxsvz

rpm's can be used alone and can be found here:

http://unixservice.com/rpm

---
unxsVZ Example

# yum install unxsvz

# #setup or get mysql info, perms, and create unxsvz db

# #first time only: install schema and sample data.
# mysql -hhost -uuser -ppasswd unxsvz < /usr/local/unxsVZ/data/unxsvz.mysqldump

